    </div>
</div>

<p>I chose a very original Jacquard jersey pencil skirt to give me a long, lean silhouette. Pairing this with <a href="https://mt.weekendmaxmara.com/new-arrival?gclsrc=aw.ds&amp;&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMI0__qpJPp5AIVEM53Ch0ECAMbEAAYASAAEgIg2fD_BwE" target="_blank">WEEKEND MAXMARA</a> sneakers in suede and leather colour blocking instantly says ‘relaxed and ready for fun’ whether you are working, holidaying or just someone who likes to be comfortable but still look very pulled together.</p>

<p><img src="/images/fashion/maxmara2/maxmara-11.jpg" alt="maxmara-11.jpg" /></p>

<p>In colder weather, I would choose either ankle or long boots to take me through winter but, for now, I am happy to show off the last of my summer tan.</p>

