    </div>
</div>

<p>Cream knitwear is another staple from <a href="https://mt.weekendmaxmara.com/new-arrival?gclsrc=aw.ds&amp;&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMI0__qpJPp5AIVEM53Ch0ECAMbEAAYASAAEgIg2fD_BwE" target="_blank">WEEKEND MAXMARA</a>. Their fabulous quality, use of natural materials – such as alpaca, silk and cashmere –and attention to detail,make every item truly beautiful in its own right.</p>

<p><img src="/images/fashion/maxmara2/maxmara-8.jpg" alt="maxmara-8.jpg" /></p>

<p>Even better, these clothes are meant to last. Whilst my ‘outfit’ is certainly fashionable, each individual item will not date and will be as gorgeous in ten years’ time as it is today. Not many brands can boast this.</p>

<div class="row no-gutters">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
